{"id":518,"date":"2018-02-28T17:49:29","date_gmt":"2018-02-28T10:49:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/bizhostvn.com\/w\/marketing\/?p=518"},"modified":"2018-02-28T17:49:29","modified_gmt":"2018-02-28T10:49:29","slug":"thuc-day-kinh-doanh-qua-viec-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/thuc-day-kinh-doanh-qua-viec-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y kinh doanh qua vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh gay g\u1eaft, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng ty kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u doanh nghi\u1ec7p. B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kinh doanh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? H\u00e3y\u00a0t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u 3 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a c\u1ee7a AJ Agrawal \u2013 Founder v\u00e0 CEO Alumnify, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kinh doanh.<\/p>\n<p><strong>1. X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Agrawal chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng: \u201cB\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y l\u1eadp ra danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong gi\u1edbi kinh doanh m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 h\u1ecd \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u00e1c m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 s\u1ebd \u201cb\u1ed1c h\u01a1i\u201d nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6750\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-6750\" src=\"http:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/1440886164_interaction.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 795px) 100vw, 795px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/1440886164_interaction.png 795w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/1440886164_interaction-300x240.png 300w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/1440886164_interaction-696x557.png 696w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/1440886164_interaction-525x420.png 525w\" alt=\"xay dung thuong hieu ca nhan\" width=\"795\" height=\"636\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng doanh nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m trong gi\u1edbi kinh doanh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5y th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n l\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n. Nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng doanh nh\u00e2n s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00f4ng ty c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>2. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u vi\u1ebft l\u00e1ch<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Vi\u1ebft l\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea1m tr\u00f9 m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p coi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u0103n, ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 hay copywriter. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a copywriter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9nh chu v\u1ec1 c\u00e2u ch\u1eef, bay b\u1ed5ng v\u1ec1 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y t\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p>Khi th\u00e0nh l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ty Alumnify, Agrawal c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n v\u00ec c\u00e1c sinh vi\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng qu\u00ean \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u vi\u1ebft blog \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb suy ngh\u0129 n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd! Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng ty anh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trung th\u00e0nh v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ecdc nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1eeb Agrawal.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng hay! Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n vi\u1ebft th\u1eadt. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc h\u00ecnh dung th\u1eadt r\u00f5 n\u00e9t v\u1ec1 b\u1ea1n. X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t doanh nh\u00e2n lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea5y.<\/p>\n<p><strong><\/p>\n<p>3. Ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 doanh nghi\u1ec7p, nh\u1eefng trang chia s\u1ebb th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 blog, c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u0169ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. B\u1ea1n \u201ctrung th\u1ef1c\u201d hay \u201cd\u1ed1i tr\u00e1\u201d, doanh nghi\u1ec7p b\u1ea1n qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00ecn v\u1edbi \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. H\u00e3y c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<\/p>\n<p>Suy ngh\u0129 k\u1ef9 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n t\u00e0i. Sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e3y ki\u00ean tr\u00ec \u0111i t\u1edbi c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p n\u00e0y. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi v\u00e0i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u201cng\u1ea5m\u201d th\u00f4ng qua h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c b\u1ea1n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6751\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-6751\" src=\"http:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan-1024x726.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan-1024x726.png 1024w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan-300x213.png 300w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan-100x70.png 100w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan-696x494.png 696w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan-1068x758.png 1068w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan-592x420.png 592w, https:\/\/blog.mediaz.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/subiz-live-chat-xay-dung-thuong-hieu-ca-nhan.png 1459w\" alt=\"xay dung thuong hieu ca nhan\" width=\"640\" height=\"454\" \/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ea1nh tranh gay g\u1eaft, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng ty kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u doanh nghi\u1ec7p. B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":519,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/518"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=518"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/518\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":520,"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/518\/revisions\/520"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/marketing.websiteviet.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/519"}